About this item

  • Enhanced Sun Protection: Shield your car interior from harmful UV rays with EcoNour’s durable car window shades. Crafted from high-quality 240T polyester, this heat shield automotive effectively blocks sunlight, keeping your vehicle cool and safeguarding your dashboard and upholstery. An essential sun visor for car for a comfortable drive.
  • Reinforced Overlapping Design: Unlike traditional window sun blockers, EcoNour features a unique overlapping design that extends up to 8 inches for a snug fit. Ideal for windshields up to 64x32 inches, this window shade for car windshield is perfect for small sedans, mini SUVs, and hatchbacks.
  • Compact and Easy to Use: This cool window sunshade easily pops open, installs in seconds, and folds away for convenient storage in the included pouch. Ideal for those seeking a hassle-free, windshield sun shade foldable solution for daily use.
  • Durability You Can Trust: Made from premium 240T polyester, this automotive heat shield offers long-lasting performance and withstands extreme heat conditions. Keep your car cooler with this reliable car sun shade windshield designed for durability.
  • Choose the Right Fit: Available in multiple sizes, EcoNour’s shades for windows are tailored to fit various vehicle models. Refer to the size chart to pick the best car window shade for maximum protection.

Product Description

Think Sun Heat, Choose EcoNour Car Windshield Sun Shades!

EcoNour Windshield Sunshade offers plenty of benefits to your car and personal health and also reduces the cabin temperature on a great scale. You don’t have to worry about the extreme internal temperatures anymore. This car shade maintains a cool and ideal car internal temperature.

EcoNour Windshield Sunshade is proven effective in diverging the heat

1. It provides effective UV, sun, and summer heat protection 2. Maintains dashboards by preventing fading and cracking 3. An easy-to-store folding design makes storage convenient 4. Within seconds, it can be installed and removed

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Customers say

    Customers find the car sunshade effective at blocking sunlight and keeping interiors 10 degrees cooler, particularly in Texas heat. The product is easy to put up and take down, and customers consider it well worth the price. The fit and foldability receive mixed feedback - while some say it's big enough, others note it's not perfect for all cars, and while some find it easy to fold up, others find it tricky to do so. The quality is also mixed, with some saying it's well made while others report poor construction.

      5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice!
      Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2025
      Size: X-LargeVerified Purchase
      The EcoNour Car Shade Front Windshield is a high-quality sun visor accessory designed to protect your car’s interior from harmful UV rays and sun heat. This product is specifically made to fit a wide range of vehicles, with an X-Large size measuring 69 x 35 inches, making it ideal for larger vehicles like SUVs and trucks. It offers an excellent solution to keep your car cooler in hot weather and prevent interior damage from prolonged sun exposure. Here's a comprehensive review based on its features, performance, and value:

      Key Features:
      Effective UV and Heat Protection:

      The EcoNour Car Shade is designed to block up to 99% of harmful UV rays. This helps to keep the temperature inside your vehicle significantly lower, even on the hottest days. By preventing direct sunlight from entering through the windshield, it not only keeps the interior cooler but also protects the dashboard, upholstery, and electronics from sun damage, such as fading and cracking.
      Large Size for Maximum Coverage:

      The X-Large size (69 x 35 inches) ensures that it fits a variety of vehicle types, particularly larger cars like SUVs, trucks, and minivans. Its generous dimensions provide extensive coverage for the front windshield, offering better protection than smaller sunshades that might leave areas exposed.
      Durable and High-Quality Material:

      The EcoNour Car Shade is made from high-quality reflective material designed to withstand the heat and sun’s rays effectively. The material is not only lightweight but also durable, ensuring long-lasting performance. It’s designed to fold up easily for compact storage and reuse, making it a convenient solution for daily use.
      Easy to Use and Install:

      The installation process is straightforward. Simply unfold the sunshade, place it on your windshield, and adjust it to fit your vehicle’s size. It is designed to be easy to install and remove, and its foldable design allows for compact storage when not in use, typically in the car’s glove compartment or door pocket.
      Reflective Surface:

      The sunshade features a reflective silver surface that bounces the sun’s rays away from the car, helping to reduce the amount of heat that enters the vehicle. This reflective design enhances its effectiveness, providing a noticeable difference in interior temperature when compared to not using a sunshade.
      Protects Interior from Heat:

      The heat protection offered by this windshield sunshade helps prevent the car’s interior from becoming unbearably hot. This is especially beneficial for those who live in areas with extreme summer temperatures, as it reduces the need for air conditioning when entering the vehicle.
      Affordable Price Point:

      The EcoNour Car Shade is offered at a reasonable price point, making it an affordable option for those looking to protect their car's interior without spending a lot of money. Given its quality and effectiveness, it provides great value for the price.
      Performance:
      Sun and Heat Protection: The EcoNour Car Shade performs exceptionally well at blocking sunlight and keeping the interior cooler. Users consistently report a noticeable reduction in temperature inside the car when using the sunshade, especially during long periods of sun exposure. This not only keeps the car comfortable but also helps prevent interior components from becoming too hot and causing discomfort when getting into the vehicle.

      UV Protection: The sunshade’s ability to block 99% of UV rays helps protect the car’s interior, including seats, dashboard, and steering wheel, from fading and damage due to prolonged exposure to the sun. This protection helps to maintain the car’s aesthetic and resale value over time.

      Ease of Use: Many users appreciate the simplicity of installation. It only takes a few seconds to install, and the foldable design makes it easy to store when not in use. It’s a hassle-free product that doesn't require any complex setup or adjustments.

      Durability: The material used in the sunshade is durable and resistant to wear, even with frequent folding and unfolding. It's designed to be resilient enough to last for several seasons, and it holds up well against exposure to sunlight and heat without showing signs of wear.

      Pros:
      Blocks up to 99% of UV rays, reducing interior heat and protecting from sun damage.
      Large X-Large size (69 x 35 inches) fits most vehicles, especially larger cars like SUVs, trucks, and minivans.
      Made from high-quality, durable reflective material for long-lasting performance.
      Easy to install and remove with a foldable design for compact storage.
      Reflective surface effectively reduces the amount of heat entering the vehicle.
      Affordable compared to other high-end sunshades on the market.
      Helps maintain a cooler interior and prevents the car from becoming unbearably hot on sunny days.
      Protects interior components (seats, dashboard) from sun damage and fading.
      Cons:
      One size may not fit all: While the X-Large size works well for most large vehicles, it may not be the perfect fit for all cars, especially those with smaller or irregularly shaped windshields.
      Does not cover side windows: The sunshade only covers the front windshield, so it does not provide protection for side windows. Some users may need to purchase additional shades for other parts of the vehicle.
      Manual adjustment required: Unlike some more advanced sunshades with automatic mechanisms, this model requires manual adjustment each time it is installed or removed, which could be a small inconvenience for some.
      Conclusion:
      The EcoNour Car Shade Front Windshield is an excellent product for anyone looking to protect their vehicle’s interior from the damaging effects of the sun. Its high-quality reflective material, UV and heat protection, and large size make it a great fit for larger vehicles like SUVs and trucks. It’s easy to install, foldable for convenient storage, and highly effective in keeping the car cooler and preventing sun damage to interior components.

      For the price, the EcoNour Car Shade provides great value, offering significant benefits in terms of comfort and interior protection. Whether you live in a hot climate or just want to keep your car cool during the summer months, this sunshade is a practical and affordable solution.
